tasks.instruction: Build CougarFanz platform by taking the existing BoyFanz codebase and replacing all BoyFanz branding with CougarFanz branding. Target demographic is women 35 and older in adult content creation. Use the research report at /workspace/cougarfanz-platform-development-strategy.md as reference. The user will provide the logo. Use Shadcn-ui, TypeScript and Tailwind CSS.
